  NBS-034 | BIRTH CERTIFICATE PDF + QR + RITA PUSH
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  Owner  : Member 1 (Backend)
  Points : 5

  USER STORY:
  As the system, after a birth is registered I generate a birth certificate
  PDF with a signed QR code and push the certificate data to RITA API.

  ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA:
  Given a birth record has been successfully created
  When the officer requests the birth certificate
