       Delivery officer name and NID
       Issue date, certificate number, signed QR code
  And the QR code payload is: { certNo, childNid, dob, issueDate, signature }
  And the PDF is stored in Cloudinary and the URL saved in births table
  And the birth data is pushed to RITA API (mock in dev)
  And rita_synced = true on success, rita_synced = false + retry queue on failure

