  [ ] Create mock RITA API at /api/mock/rita/births for dev environment
  [ ] Push to RITA: POST {rita_url}/births with certificate data
  [ ] On RITA push success: update births.rita_synced = true
  [ ] On RITA push fail: log error, add to retry queue (node-cron retry every 1hr)
  [ ] Create POST /api/births/:birthId/certificate route
